{"tid":1234291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[非割𥱊 但留意監察] 但務必小心5:0 林卓廷行為","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:39:38.000Z","uid":7971,"like":647,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"be4c062512b11bef4647bb79b5c337509d370b70","tid":1234291,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"林卓廷同糾察 我屌你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233619</a><br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n成個民主黨今次嘅表現真係好值得大家欣賞<br />\n特別係鄺仔 明顯係真誠為香港<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我覺得一個人如果真誠對件事好<br />\n就算大家手法唔同 但只要方向一致<br />\n都係各自爬手 目標為本</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但林依個人 真係要小心小心同小心<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢琴晚嘅發言 真係完全帶頭破壞 <br />\n依家大家互相嘅努力<br />\n係真係同食左一個有人血嘅 人血饅頭</span></span><br />\n依個人 佢嘅行為 心態 真係只求自己上位同光環<br />\n詳情 可睇下面條link <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">59人退出民主黨 矛頭直指林卓廷</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181212/59023398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59023398&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=3ae39e22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181212%2F59023398&h=faa430a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181212/59023398</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">只少連大中華膠 胡志偉 我都覺得可信</span></span></strong><br />\n但林真係唔好盡信<br />\n你會見到根本連民主黨 黨內人士都唔信佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係割𥱊 但一定要監察 小心佢嘅行為</span></span>"},{"pid":"91ef16a8681f3eacf96fb71667ac26c5a60917c4","tid":1234291,"uid":7971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:30:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"692815b7dcb05c7f